    "id": "mindful-path-design",
    "name": "Mindful Path Design",
    "description": "Create a modern website for a psychologist called “Mindful Path Therapy”.\n\nService:\nOnline and in-person therapy for young professionals experiencing burnout and anxiety.\n\nAudience:\nPeople aged 25–45 seeking balance and mental clarity.\n\nTone:\nSupportive, modern, trustworthy, gentle.\n\nMain colors:\n- Dusty blue (primary)\n- Soft lavender accents\n- White backgrounds\n- Light gray for contrast sections\n\nGoals:\nGet visitors to book a discovery call.\n\nStructure:\n- Hero with supportive headline\n- Short intro about the therapist\n- Services offered\n- Benefits of therapy\n- Testimonials\n- Simple pricing or session info\n- Booking CTA\n\nDesign guidance:\n- Clean and modern\n- Soft rounded visuals\n- Calm lifestyle imagery\n- No aggressive sales elements\n\nCopy guidance:\n- Gentle, relatable language\n- Focus on well-being and growth\n- Avoid medical jargon\n- Make therapy feel approachable\n\nMake the page feel safe, modern, and trustworthy.\nKeep it conversion-focused but human.",
